com.oracle.svm.core.annotate

Annotation Type Inject


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Inject
    Injects the annotated field into the TargetClass. The field must not be declared static. If instances of the target class are in the image heap, the field also needs to be annotated with RecomputeFieldValue to provide a value for the injected field.
    Since:
    22.3
